# Normalize all text files to LF in the repo and on checkout.
# Reason: Node/agent tooling always writes LF; Windows core.autocrlf=true was
# fighting that, so every asset script run re-flipped tracked files to "modified"
# with a pure line-ending diff (no content change). This ends the tug-of-war.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary — never touch line endings, never text-diff.
*.png binary
*.ico binary
